<h3>Card Block Vertical</h3>
A block construct for layout. A block is a wrapper that allows your content to exist as a cell within a larger grid.
When passed a "vertical" class the block has column characteristics and vertical flow.

<h4>
{{#link-to 'examples.card-block'}}See also card block (default){{/link-to}}
</h4>

<pre>
\{{#card-block}}
\{{yield}}
\{{/card-block}}
</pre>

